I have nothin' worth stealing,
but thanks for the concern.

34:36.855 --> 34:39.222
Now fuck off.

34:47.966 --> 34:50.800
Fuckin' hell, mate.

34:53.338 --> 34:54.472
What's he doing?

34:54.473 --> 34:56.407
He's just standing there,
looking at us.

34:56.408 --> 35:00.743
Bet he can go days
without food or water.

35:14.459 --> 35:16.861
Nice of you to drop by.

35:16.862 --> 35:20.063
It's been a while.

35:20.966 --> 35:23.334
Do you know him?

35:23.335 --> 35:24.802
No.

35:24.803 --> 35:26.937
You boys hungry?

35:26.938 --> 35:28.939
I'm starving.

35:28.940 --> 35:32.809
I'm thinking
of cooking a chicken.

35:32.878 --> 35:34.478
I fuckin' love chicken.

35:34.479 --> 35:41.651
Good. Go out back and kill
whichever one takes your fancy.

35:43.622 --> 35:44.789
Kill?

35:44.790 --> 35:48.492
Get him, get him, get him!

35:48.493 --> 35:51.661
Aye! Jesus!

35:54.800 --> 35:56.534
Fuck!

35:56.535 --> 35:58.869
God!

35:58.870 --> 36:02.572
Hey-hey! Whoo-hoo!

36:15.821 --> 36:17.955
Go on. Do it.

36:17.956 --> 36:19.490
I can't.

36:19.491 --> 36:20.925
It's looking right at me.

36:20.926 --> 36:23.594
It's just a chicken.
Stop being a wuss.

36:23.595 --> 36:26.497
It reminds me
a little bit of me.

36:26.498 --> 36:27.898
What? How?

36:27.899 --> 36:30.868
The way it's staring.

36:30.869 --> 36:33.971
You know, sort of
a confused look, like...

36:33.972 --> 36:37.742
..like it doesn't really know
what's going on half the time.

36:37.743 --> 36:40.678
He's not dyin'!

36:40.679 --> 36:43.447
- He's too strong.
- You need to pull it hard, like.

36:43.448 --> 36:45.416
Then he'll start
bleeding out the front.

36:45.417 --> 36:47.952
No, he won't.
Just pull his neck.

36:47.953 --> 36:50.019
One, two, three.

36:51.757 --> 36:53.090
- He's dead?
- He's dead.

36:53.091 --> 36:55.526
- He's dead. Alright.
- Put him in the bucket.

36:55.527 --> 36:59.862
Put him in the bucket.
That's it.

37:02.667 --> 37:05.335
He's still alive, boy.

37:10.609 --> 37:14.645
What if you hold his neck
and I pull his body backwards?

37:14.646 --> 37:17.313
That sounds fair.

37:21.052 --> 37:25.655
As soon as his legs
stop kicking, pluck him.

37:33.899 --> 37:37.834
He did say "pluck him", right?

37:39.538 --> 37:42.740
<i>When you live in the city,
you don't see many animals die.</i>

37:42.741 --> 37:46.643
<i>They're all dead
when they get there.</i>

37:47.446 --> 37:49.480
<i>It didn't seem
to bother Jock much.</i>

37:49.481 --> 37:53.082
<i>He had other things on his mind.</i>

38:03.195 --> 38:06.230
<i>You know, when you've only got
one thing on your mind,</i>

38:06.231 --> 38:08.899
<i>it can be kind of hard
to think clearly.</i>

38:08.900 --> 38:11.034
<i>You can get tunnel vision.</i>

38:11.870 --> 38:16.540
<i>But if you stop
and open your eyes</i>

38:16.541 --> 38:18.975
<i>just for a moment...</i>

38:23.682 --> 38:28.017
<i>..you'd be amazed
at what you might see.</i>

38:28.119 --> 38:31.054
The hell is that?

38:31.223 --> 38:34.057
Look at that.

38:48.273 --> 38:50.741
What is it?

38:50.742 --> 38:54.177
And you made me
throw away my phone.

38:55.547 --> 38:56.814
GPS?

38:56.815 --> 38:59.982
I knew he had to be cheating!

39:00.619 --> 39:02.286
I've got an idea.

39:02.287 --> 39:06.889
<i>That was rare enough for me
so I was delighted with meself.</i>

39:40.225 --> 39:43.426
The chicken is lovely,
isn't it, Conor?

39:52.938 --> 39:56.607
It's alright. Leave it,
leave it. It's alright.

39:56.608 --> 39:59.310
Hey, thanks
for helping us there earlier.

39:59.311 --> 40:00.611
Yeah.

40:00.612 --> 40:01.879
Yeah, nice that you let us in.

40:01.880 --> 40:05.114
Could've been some other
cranky fucker, you know?

40:05.650 --> 40:08.117
What are you staring at?

40:09.588 --> 40:10.854
I'm not staring.

40:10.855 --> 40:12.656
You're staring straight at me!

40:12.657 --> 40:14.825
I'm not staring.
I'm just looking at you.

40:14.826 --> 40:16.894
I'm having
a conversation with you.

40:16.895 --> 40:20.898
Fucking hell, it'd be weird
if we didn't, like.

40:20.899 --> 40:23.334
Do you think this is funny?

40:23.335 --> 40:25.669
No, it's... No, sir.

40:25.670 --> 40:26.837
Dopey little prick.

40:26.838 --> 40:29.607
- Don't call him a dope.
- Don't you shout at me!

40:29.608 --> 40:32.276
I'm not fuckin' shouting.
I said don't call him a dope!

40:32.277 --> 40:37.314
Every time you come down here,
it is the same fuckin' shit.

40:37.315 --> 40:38.682
We've never been here before.

40:38.683 --> 40:41.986
I paid for everything.
I put you two through college.

40:41.987 --> 40:45.155
We're 15! I didn't even
pass me junior cert.

40:45.156 --> 40:47.725
- Who do you think we are?
- For fuck's...

40:47.726 --> 40:49.126
You've had enough
of that now, alright?

40:49.127 --> 40:52.162
Fuck you, I've had enough!
This is my fuckin' house.

40:52.163 --> 40:55.366
- I'll drink whatever I like.
- Sit down and eat your dinner.

40:55.367 --> 40:57.267
That's my fuckin' whiskey.
Give it to me.

40:57.268 --> 41:00.170
- Get off me!
- Give me that fuckin' bottle!

41:00.171 --> 41:02.471
Get away from us!

41:02.941 --> 41:03.941
Stay back there.

41:03.942 --> 41:05.943
Get out of the way,
you little prick.

41:05.944 --> 41:07.745
- Alright, stop, stop!
- What?

41:07.746 --> 41:10.114
- What are you saying?
- Relax, alright, boy?

41:10.115 --> 41:12.082
OK, I'm gonna put the chair down

41:12.083 --> 41:14.918
and we're gonna talk, alright?

41:14.919 --> 41:17.154
Alright.

41:17.155 --> 41:18.989
Stay back.

41:18.990 --> 41:21.325
Fuckin' hell!
Don't touch it, ya cunt!

41:21.326 --> 41:23.227
<i>I went through
all the options in me head</i>

41:23.228 --> 41:27.063
<i>and there was only
one logical thing for us to do.</i>

41:29.000 --> 41:30.834
Relax! Relax!

41:30.835 --> 41:32.970
No, no!

41:32.971 --> 41:34.371
I'm here! Look!

41:34.372 --> 41:37.207
Look. Stop. Stop.

41:37.208 --> 41:39.043
Isn't this a nice comfy chair?

41:39.044 --> 41:41.679
- Do you like this? Yeah?
- Yeah.

41:41.680 --> 41:43.747
You've just gotta talk
to him and he's grand.

41:43.748 --> 41:46.717
- Give me the bottle.
- You can't have that, alright?

41:46.718 --> 41:49.820
We'll give you something later,
like a beer or something.

41:49.821 --> 41:53.791
- Alright, alright.
- See? He wants a beer, boy.

41:53.792 --> 41:56.092
Yeah.

41:57.328 --> 42:00.330
<i>That night sitting around
watching telly</i>

42:00.331 --> 42:01.799
<i>was the closest we had all got</i>

42:01.800 --> 42:04.768
<i>to a normal night in
for a long, long time.</i>

42:04.769 --> 42:07.036
Yeah, that show is very good.

42:11.910 --> 42:13.844
<i>I think sometimes
people do the opposite</i>

42:13.845 --> 42:17.014
<i>of what they should do
when they're lonely.</i>

42:17.015 --> 42:18.882
<i>The hide away at work,</i>

42:18.883 --> 42:22.052
<i>fight with the people
they miss most,</i>

42:22.053 --> 42:23.954
<i>and they turn to the bottle</i>

42:23.955 --> 42:28.157
<i>instead of pickin' up the phone.</i>

42:47.412 --> 42:50.180
<i>Imagine you've been
out all night,</i>

42:50.181 --> 42:53.083
<i>no sleep, no food.</i>

42:53.084 --> 42:55.886
<i>You're in the same wet clothes.</i>

42:55.887 --> 42:58.122
<i>Same stupid face.</i>

42:58.123 --> 43:00.423
Fuck...

43:01.493 --> 43:07.164
<i>You stuck in there
in spite of everything.</i>

43:07.165 --> 43:08.432
<i>At least when it's all over,</i>

43:08.433 --> 43:12.035
<i>you can take pleasure in
knowing it was all worthwhile.</i>

43:12.036 --> 43:17.073
No, no, no.
No, no, no, no, no...

43:21.312 --> 43:22.012
FUC...!

43:22.013 --> 43:24.448
Our treasure's waiting
for us around this corner,

43:24.449 --> 43:27.317
but there's gonna be loads
of guards, drug squad,

43:27.318 --> 43:29.520
special forces, helicopters,

43:29.521 --> 43:31.522
probably even the army.

43:31.523 --> 43:33.123
Should we use fake names?

43:33.124 --> 43:35.159
Would you stop
with the fake names?

43:35.160 --> 43:39.062
Look, if anyone asks,
just say we're on holidays.

43:39.063 --> 43:42.732
- Got it?
- Yeah, got it.

43:49.841 --> 43:54.443
Nah, this... this
can't be the place.

44:06.024 --> 44:08.992
Here, sorry.
Is this Three Castle Head?

44:08.993 --> 44:13.430
- Yeah.
- We're just on our holidays.

44:13.431 --> 44:15.365
You should've seen
the place yesterday.

44:15.366 --> 44:17.501
You heard about
the cocaine seizure?

44:17.502 --> 44:19.069
No... no. What was that?

44:19.070 --> 44:21.238
Have you been
hiding under a rock?

44:21.239 --> 44:24.074
The guards found
61 bales of cocaine.

44:24.075 --> 44:25.342
440 million euro worth.

44:25.343 --> 44:28.245
- They got it all?
- Yep, every last one.

44:28.246 --> 44:32.448
There won't be any parties
in this country for a while.

44:32.584 --> 44:35.785
Well, that's not good.

44:36.888 --> 44:41.590
FUCK!

45:12.490 --> 45:15.926
<i>Jock was taking the news
that our treasure was gone</i>

45:15.927 --> 45:16.660
<i>better than I expected.</i>

45:16.661 --> 45:20.197
I'm not crying, boy.
It's just hay fever.

45:20.198 --> 45:21.932
Weren't gonna say nothing.

45:21.933 --> 45:25.903
There's so much grass
around here.

45:25.904 --> 45:30.339
The pollen count is really
high as well at the moment.

45:34.312 --> 45:36.280
What's wrong with ya?

45:36.281 --> 45:40.316
I've just gotta take
a wilder-poo, like.

45:40.485 --> 45:41.518
A 'wilder-poo'?

45:41.519 --> 45:44.321
Yeah, boy, I haven't
gone since Cork.

45:44.322 --> 45:46.189
What's a wilder-poo?

45:46.190 --> 45:50.193
It's when you take
a shit outside, like.

45:50.194 --> 45:52.162
You know, a wilderness poo.

45:52.163 --> 45:56.566
- A poo in the wilderness?
- Yeah.

45:56.567 --> 46:00.436
Well, just go, then.
There's no-one here.

46:00.438 --> 46:02.472
But you're here, right?

46:02.473 --> 46:04.174
I'm not gonna look.

46:04.175 --> 46:06.944
I hardly wanna
see you taking a shit.

46:06.945 --> 46:09.413
Alright.
That's not what I meant.

46:09.414 --> 46:13.415
I just need a bit of privacy.
That's all.

46:14.252 --> 46:16.919
I'll be back in a minute.

46:21.392 --> 46:24.760
Jesus. Fuck.

46:53.992 --> 46:56.326
Jock! Come here.

46:56.327 --> 46:58.595
I don't wanna look at your poo.

46:58.596 --> 47:01.864
Just come here a second.

47:03.301 --> 47:05.168
- What is it, boy?
- No!

47:05.169 --> 47:08.537
Don't say a word.

47:11.109 --> 47:13.477
Come on.

47:13.478 --> 47:16.412
Be very quiet.

47:33.498 --> 47:36.199
Holy shit!

47:36.200 --> 47:39.336
He must be
one of them gang members.

47:39.337 --> 47:42.571
Has he got what
I think he's got?

47:44.642 --> 47:48.277
Our treasure.

47:48.613 --> 47:51.415
Fuck, yeah!
You fucker!

47:51.416 --> 47:53.949
Fuck.

47:58.790 --> 48:00.357
- Yo.
- Psst!

48:00.358 --> 48:02.759
He's alive, but he's passed out.

48:02.760 --> 48:04.494
He's bate.

48:04.495 --> 48:07.830
Look, he's got a gammy arm.

48:11.536 --> 48:14.603
He's got a gammy leg too.

48:17.308 --> 48:19.708
He's handicap.

48:20.144 --> 48:22.612
Poor fella.

48:22.613 --> 48:26.149
That'll make it easier.
So come on. Give me a hand.

48:26.150 --> 48:29.186
I'm not stealing
from a handicapped fella.

48:29.187 --> 48:30.387
He's a drug dealer.

48:30.388 --> 48:32.355
What difference does it make
if he's handicapped?

48:32.356 --> 48:34.524
It's like we're being faced
with Stephen Hawking.

48:34.525 --> 48:38.361
This is his chair. You don't
say, "Let's take his chair."

48:38.362 --> 48:39.596
Stephen Hawking?
Who's he again?

48:39.597 --> 48:42.732
The smart guy who's so smart,
he can't walk or talk.

48:42.733 --> 48:44.768
- Do you not know this fella?
- No.

48:44.769 --> 48:47.304
"I am gonna invent
the universe."

48:47.305 --> 48:49.573
He speaks like
he's, like, sucking in.

48:49.574 --> 48:51.141
He's like, "I'm..." Like...

48:51.142 --> 48:55.644
This is what we came for.
We're not leaving without it.

49:00.418 --> 49:04.421
He's probably
holding onto it for warmth.

49:04.422 --> 49:07.489
It's cocaine,
not a hot water bottle.

49:08.459 --> 49:09.860
If he wakes up, we're dead.

49:09.861 --> 49:13.296
- He won't wake up.
- Why are you whispering then?

49:13.297 --> 49:15.265
I'm not whispering.

49:15.266 --> 49:18.701
For fuck's sake!

49:49.200 --> 49:51.735
He's freezing, boy.
We can't just leave him here.

49:51.736 --> 49:53.336
When we're far enough away,

49:53.337 --> 49:57.139
we'll leave an anonymous
phone call for the guards.

50:19.564 --> 50:21.831
Jesus!

50:21.832 --> 50:23.800
Stop yelling! You'll wake him!

50:23.801 --> 50:26.702
He IS fuckin' awake!

50:26.704 --> 50:28.939
- Arggh!
- Arggh! Shit!

50:28.940 --> 50:30.373
Get off!

50:30.374 --> 50:33.942
No! Go... go back
to sleep, please! Fuck!

50:35.213 --> 50:37.414
Fuck! Give me my bag!

50:37.415 --> 50:41.784
Go on! Please! Go!

50:55.800 --> 50:57.234
<i>I never really believed</i>

50:57.235 --> 50:58.702
<i>we would find
that bale of cocaine.</i>

50:58.703 --> 51:02.005
<i>For me, it was just one of them
adventures you go on,</i>

51:02.006 --> 51:03.673
<i>like looking for your G-spot.</i>

51:03.674 --> 51:05.408
<i>You don't really
believe it exists</i>

51:05.409 --> 51:09.279
<i>and you're not sure what
to do with it if you find it.</i>

51:09.280 --> 51:11.281
We did it, kid. We did it!

51:11.282 --> 51:12.648
We sure did, boy!

51:24.629 --> 51:26.029
<i>For Jock, it's different.</i>

51:26.030 --> 51:30.632
<i>Finding that coke
is the only bit of hope he has.</i>

52:08.973 --> 52:11.308
Do you wanna have a gasp
and a drink?

52:11.309 --> 52:12.676
I'd really love one. Thanks.

52:12.677 --> 52:16.612
Mind the bike
while I'm doing this.

52:33.464 --> 52:37.000
Fuck! Shit!

52:37.001 --> 52:39.369
- What the...
- What's going on?

52:39.370 --> 52:41.705
It's gone. It must have
got cut on something.

52:41.706 --> 52:42.539
What do you mean, it got cut?

52:42.540 --> 52:47.377
- There's a hole in the bottom!
- There's a hole in it?

52:47.378 --> 52:48.712
- Look...
- But it's all gone.

52:48.713 --> 52:50.547
I don't know where.
I'm sorry, alright?

52:50.548 --> 52:53.083
Seven million euros worth
of cocaine pour out this bag?

52:53.084 --> 52:54.784
How didn't you notice
it getting lighter?!

52:54.785 --> 52:57.854
How didn't you notice it
coming off the back of my bike?!

52:57.855 --> 52:59.622
'Cause that wasn't
my fuckin' job!

52:59.623 --> 53:03.560
- I gave it to you to look after!
- You have eyes, don't you?

53:03.561 --> 53:06.463
You're some dopey prick,
you know that?

53:06.464 --> 53:08.898
Alright, but don't call me that.

53:08.899 --> 53:10.834
Why not? It's what you are.

53:10.835 --> 53:12.702
I'd rather be a dopey prick

53:12.703 --> 53:16.605
than a devious scumbag like you.

54:32.483 --> 54:35.117
It's too fuckin' tight!

54:35.653 --> 54:38.221
If it isn't Lance Armstrong!

54:38.222 --> 54:40.089
Where the fuck have you been?

54:40.090 --> 54:43.959
Here. Do some real police work.

54:44.161 --> 54:46.862
Who's next there?

54:48.199 --> 54:50.967
I want to report me son missing.
He's not answering his phone.

54:50.968 --> 54:56.004
He's been gone since yesterday.
That's a photo of him there.

55:00.177 --> 55:02.512
I'm gonna catch you
and lock you up

55:02.513 --> 55:04.581
where you belong,
you thieving knacker!

55:04.582 --> 55:07.916
Watch who you callin' knacker.

55:13.591 --> 55:16.192
<i>Do you remember
that prick Billy Murphy?</i>

55:16.193 --> 55:17.894
<i>Well, his time
in the slammer was up</i>

55:17.895 --> 55:21.064
<i>and while inside, he had
a cellmate with a big mouth.</i>

55:21.065 --> 55:23.132
Did I hear something
about a fella going around

55:23.133 --> 55:24.834
wearing your face as a mask
or something?

55:24.835 --> 55:27.537
<i>According to this big mouth,
Jock was flah'ing his sister.</i>

55:27.538 --> 55:30.707
<i>Halfway through, he put on
his fake Billy mask as a joke,</i>

55:30.708 --> 55:32.609
<i>but she didn't
find it very funny.</i>

55:32.610 --> 55:34.577
I hear this screamin'
coming from upstairs

55:34.578 --> 55:36.012
from me sister's room - "Arggh!"

55:36.013 --> 55:38.982
It was just a joke!

55:38.983 --> 55:40.683
"Arggh!"

55:40.684 --> 55:42.018
How's it going?

55:42.019 --> 55:45.021
- Who the fuck was that?!
- None of your business.

55:45.022 --> 55:48.525
<i>Big mouth put two and two
together and got five.</i>

55:48.526 --> 55:53.995
Fake Billy's real name
is Conor MacSweeney.

55:55.833 --> 55:57.867
<i>Billy Murphy's friends
consist of people</i>

55:57.868 --> 55:59.802
<i>he has previously
beaten the shit out of</i>

55:59.803 --> 56:02.871
<i>and they're too scared
not to be his friends.</i>

56:06.176 --> 56:07.143
Shit.

56:07.144 --> 56:08.711
I've been fuckin'
looking for you!

56:08.712 --> 56:10.813
- You little fuckin' prick!
- Fuck off, will ya?

56:10.814 --> 56:12.248
Come here!
Come here, you little shit!

56:12.249 --> 56:14.951
- What are you doing, Billy?
- You're fuckin' dead!

56:14.952 --> 56:18.655
You hear me?
You're fuckin' dead!

56:18.656 --> 56:20.690
Why didn't you fuckin'
tell me it was him?

56:20.691 --> 56:23.626
You're fuckin' useless.
Yeah, look at the ground.

56:23.627 --> 56:25.127
Look at the fuckin' ground.

56:45.082 --> 56:46.214
Dad, are you home?

56:51.822 --> 56:54.489
Nice of you
to finally come home.

56:54.925 --> 56:58.094
You're not gonna tell me
where you've been?

56:58.095 --> 57:01.563
Back here
when I'm talking to you.

57:15.346 --> 57:18.948
The least you can do is offer me
some half-arsed excuse!

57:18.949 --> 57:20.383
Just leave me alone!

57:20.384 --> 57:23.485
What happened to your face?

57:25.222 --> 57:26.555
Nothing.

57:42.373 --> 57:43.973
Are you alright?

57:43.974 --> 57:46.042
Look, I'm grand.

57:46.043 --> 57:49.945
Alright?
I just wanna be left alone.

57:56.186 --> 57:57.285
Fine.

58:31.955 --> 58:35.024
How are you, love? Is the
battery pre-charged in this?

58:35.025 --> 58:37.226
Should be.
Stick in the gas canister

58:37.227 --> 58:40.562
and you'll hear a pump if it is.

58:50.974 --> 58:53.375
What are you making?

58:53.377 --> 58:56.111
I'm not making anything.

58:56.146 --> 58:59.414
What's the nail gun for?

58:59.883 --> 59:02.617
For torturing people.

59:14.331 --> 59:17.133
That's good.

