01:18:16.072 --> 01:18:18.139
<i>Well, most of it, anyway.</i>

01:18:18.140 --> 01:18:20.508
<i>I did have to adjust the facts
a bit for the telly.</i>

01:18:20.509 --> 01:18:23.478
