like Sergeant Healy,

01:18:23.479 --> 01:18:27.415
er, to protect us from dangerous
criminals. He's our hero.

01:18:27.416 --> 01:18:29.317
<i>Healy tried to get them facts
straightened out,</i>

01:18:29.318 --> 01:18:32.087
<i>but his superintendent
didn't seem to give a shit.</i>

01:18:32.088 --> 01:18:33.221
The station needs the publicity.

01:18:33.222 --> 01:18:36.124
It's a great story,
so shut the fuck up

01:18:36.125 --> 01:18:37.893
and take the promotion.

01:18:37.894 --> 01:18:39.294
And no more bicycles.

01:18:39.295 --> 01:18:42.097
<i>Jock had his day in court
for stealing bikes.</i>

01:18:42.098 --> 01:18:43.899
<i>He was given
a suspended sentence</i>

01:18:43.900 --> 01:18:45.333
<i>because of
his abusive upbringing</i>

01:18:45.334 --> 01:18:47.501
<i>and was placed into foster care.</i>

01:18:49.171 --> 01:18:51.373
<i>And guess who became
a foster parent -</i>

01:18:51.374 --> 01:18:53.208
<i>with great reluctance,
I might add.</i>

01:18:53.209 --> 01:18:55.510
That's some useless bollocks.
Look.

01:18:55.511 --> 01:18:57.012
You on the jammy rag or what?

01:18:57.013 --> 01:18:58.947
<i>It was nice
that she had someone else</i>

01:18:58.948 --> 01:19:00.515
<i>to yell at other than me
for a change.</i>

01:19:00.516 --> 01:19:03.218
- I'm your son now.
- You're not my son!

01:19:03.219 --> 01:19:05.220
- I am your son.
- I didn't adopt you.

01:19:05.221 --> 01:19:06.254
- I love you.
- My God.

01:19:06.255 --> 01:19:08.290
<i>Billy Murphy
found himself back in prison.</i>

01:19:08.291 --> 01:19:10.659
- Did you find your man?
<i>- This time for attempted murder</i>

01:19:10.660 --> 01:19:13.295
<i>so we won't be seeing him
for a while.</i>

01:19:13.296 --> 01:19:15.096
<i>Mam visited the local butcher</i>

01:19:15.097 --> 01:19:17.098
<i>and finally got
her gammy tooth sorted.</i>

01:19:17.099 --> 01:19:20.535
<i>I don't envy that fella.
As for me...</i>

01:19:20.536 --> 01:19:23.004
Alright, this mackerel here
came from over that hill

01:19:23.005 --> 01:19:24.105
and only took 20 minutes
to get here.

01:19:24.106 --> 01:19:27.309
- That's how fresh it is.
- Alright. Go on. Give me four.

01:19:27.310 --> 01:19:29.945
So what else are you selling
that's local?

01:19:29.946 --> 01:19:31.146
You're looking at it, but.

01:19:31.147 --> 01:19:32.013
Sure I can get that for free.

01:19:32.014 --> 01:19:36.184
<i>Where one treasure hunt
ends, another one begins.</i>

01:19:36.185 --> 01:19:39.054
