You interested?

01:19:39.055 --> 01:19:41.323
- Alright. Go on.
- This is an oyster.

01:19:41.324 --> 01:19:42.090
A delicacy really.

01:19:42.091 --> 01:19:44.426
People call me the oyster
of the land because, you know,

01:19:44.427 --> 01:19:48.964
my hard exterior and soft,
emotional interior, do you know?

01:19:48.965 --> 01:19:51.666
Pulling that shit again?
"You're looking at it."

01:19:51.667 --> 01:19:55.036
At least he's not
a fucking streak of misery.

01:19:55.037 --> 01:19:57.973
A streak of misery?
Hrrrgh.

01:19:57.974 --> 01:19:59.174
- Is that how I look?
- Yeah.

01:19:59.175 --> 01:20:01.343
Excuse me.
You want a fish, dear? Hrrnggh?

01:20:01.344 --> 01:20:04.578
- Is that what I'm like?
- Shut up.
